{"word":"στατίζω","slug":"στατίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στατίζω</b></el> <el>(στᾰτίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>poetic for <a href='S:ἵστημι'><el>ἵστημι</el></a>\n<p/><i>to place</i>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> = <el>ἵσταμαι</el>, <i>to stand</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—so also <a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}